║                         <Gradients>                          ║
╠═════════════════════════════╦════════════════════════════════╣
║     [33] red_to_yellow      ║     [42] cyan_to_blue          ║
║     [34] yellow_to_red      ║     [43] blue_to_purple        ║
║     [35] red_to_purple      ║     [44] purple_to_blue        ║
║     [36] purple_to_red      ║     [45] red_to_blue           ║
║     [37] green_to_yellow    ║     [46] blue_to_red           ║
